reviews.review_text: speedy speedy Great sound but it seems the boys were enhanced in more ways than one and are rushing to the finish line. Help->Slip especially feels like extremely rushed. During Saturday Night Bobby has trouble catching up with lyrics. Noteworthy Eyes however with Jerry stretching out in the jam with some stellar soloing.

Uptempo for sure It does seem like they're all a little coked out. I suspect that the previous night's magic did all of them in a bit.

I generally prefer SBDs, but as other reviewers have pointed out, the P.A. mix had very little Jerry and a lot of Brent, so these Quirk AUDs give a more balanced picture of what it really sounded like at the Greek.
better then 3 stars much better I think
